        <section class="css-stuff">
          <h2>Projects</h2>
          <p>
            I've not worked on many yet but there's
            <a href="https://kololianet.vercel.app" target="_blank"
              >kololianet</a
            >, a company website written in REACT and
            <a href="https://kinambaref.netlify.app" target="_blank"
